<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB09049</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT REORGANIZING THE COMELEC OFFICES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Proposes to address the notable disparity between the Commission's employee's salary against that of other government agencies, despite possessing similar qualifications and are in equivalent positions.

Provides for the Commission's field offices such as: a. Regional Election Office; b. Provincial Election Office; c. The National Capital Region; and City/Municipal Office.

